4. AUTHORIZED USE

The only uses permitted without express written authorization from the Author
are:

  a) Private, local inspection and technical review of the source code for the
     sole purpose of evaluating the protocol for a potential collaboration,
     partnership, or investment with Stefan Antonio Cirisanu and humanityledger.

  b) Forking the repository on GitHub exclusively for the purpose of submitting
     a pull request with a proposed contribution to the official repository
     maintained by humanityledger. Any such fork must be closed or deleted if
     the pull request is not merged within 30 days.

  c) Reference to the Software in academic or journalistic writing, provided
     that full attribution is given to Stefan Antonio Cirisanu and
     humanityledger, and that no substantial portion of the source code is
     reproduced.

